---
import { ArrowRight, ClipboardList } from "lucide-react";
---
<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="lg:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">How to Prepare a Project Brief</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
          You don't need every answer immediately. Providing this context helps TheEduAssist recommend a practical starting point.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-semibold rounded-md text-white bg-brand-navy hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-brand-navy">
          Share Your Project Requirements
          <ArrowRight className="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-2/3 bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
         <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
            <ul class="space-y-3">
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Organizational objective and target audiences</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">The specific business or learning problem</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Current state of content and platforms</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Desired delivery format and course volume</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Stakeholder groups involved in approval</span></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Target languages or regions</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Technical or accessibility constraints</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Data, security, or privacy requirements</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Target timing and required procurement process</span></li>
               <li class="flex items-start"><ClipboardList className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green mr-2 mt-0.5 shrink-0" /><span class="text-slate-700">Availability of subject-matter experts</span></li>
            </ul>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
